title: Education Week
description:
Education Week is your source for compelling videos on K-12 education, including powerful stories about schools across the nation, news coverage, explainers, unique perspectives on education debates, and profiles of exemplary educators. 

About Education Week:
Education Week (edweek.org) is America’s most trusted source of independent K-12 education news, analysis, and opinion, with comprehensive coverage of education policy and practice in print, on the web, in video, and via live and virtual events. Our work serves to raise the level of understanding and discourse about education among policymakers, school and district leaders, teachers, researchers, and the public. Education Week has been providing award-winning coverage of the field for over 35 years.

Interested in licensing? Contact reprints@epe.org

title: Andrew and Megan - Indefinite Travel
description:
Hi, we're Andrew and Megan of Indefinite Travel! We've been location independent for the last 5 years. It only took us about 5 years and about a billion people asking "did you film it?!" to figure out, hmmm... let's start a Travel Channel!

So, here we are! As a travel couple we've managed to squeeze all our belongings in 1 shared suitcase and 2 backpacks. We survive off of flight miles, Airbnb's, lots off coffee and donuts. Our absolute favorite thing on earth is to hear when we've inspired someone else to live a life by design and pack up to travel in their own way. Follow us as we check off a never ending bucket-list around the world!

Stop by and say "hi!", find us on a corner of the internet and let us know where you're from and what's your favorite travel destination!
